photo-scripts
Copyright (c) 2009, Martin Engelmann <martin.engelmann@gmx.de>

This is a set of scripts to edit a collection of photos. It consits of the
following scripts and modules:
 * adjust-time.pl
   Corrects the CreateDate exif tag in a number of files. 

 * Photo.pm
 	Module with some routines used by multiple scripts.

 * DateTime/Format/Exif.pm
 	Helper class to parse timestamps in the exif tags to DateTime objects and
	format them again

Dependencies:
 * DateTime::Format::Builder
 * DateTime::Format::Duration
 * DateTime::Format::Exif
 * DateTime::Format::ISO8601
 * Image::ExifTool

